    <td width="570" valign="top"><p class="smallheading"><br>
      About DB </p>
      <p class="bookmarcbody"><strong>Designer Bookbinders</strong> is
        one of the foremost societies devoted to the craft of fine bookbinding.
        Founded over fifty years ago it has, by means of exhibitions and publications,
        helped to establish the reputation of British bookbinding worldwide.
        Its membership includes some of the most highly regarded makers in the
        fields
        of fine bookbinding, book arts and artists&#8217; books, each with a
      passion for presenting the bound text as a unique art object.</p>
